ISLAMABAD, Jan 06 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Friday expressed deep grief and sorrow over demise of Haji Yaqub, the father-in-law of senior journalist Khalid Mahmood.
The minister, in a condolence message, prayed to the Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the irreparable loss with fortitude.
